State üçç

Provides reactivity states

Usage ‚ö°

var
  lvl = remember 1
  exp = remember 0
  maxExp = remember 10
  name = remember "Ethosa"

appRoutes("app"):
  "/":
    tDiv:
      "Hello, {name}, your level is {lvl} [{exp}/{maxExp}]"
    tButton:
      "Increase exp"
      @click:
        exp += 1
        while exp >= maxExp:
          exp -= maxExp
          lvl += 1
          maxExp += 5
